description:
In this week’s episode, Anna is joined by Ike Barinholtz, the hilarious, scene-stealing star of “The Mindy Project,” “Sisters,” “Neighbors” and more. Listen in as Ike and Anna compare 80’s crushes, discuss magicians’ sexual prowess (or lack thereof), and role-play awkward date scenarios. Ike also shares his most embarrassing date moment: the night he met his now-wife’s parents! Later, the gang tries to help a female listener cope with her fiance's declining sex drive. And be sure to stay tuned until the end of the call, when Ike asks his own question – and gets a very unexpected answer.

Hosted on Acast. See acast.com/privacy for more information.
